Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/guardianwiressubCaroline Jurie yanked the crown off Pushpika de Silva minutes after she was declared ‚ÄúMrs Sri Lanka 2020‚Äù during a gala in Colombo on April 4. Jurie declared that Pushpika de Silva was ineligible as the winner because she was divorced, and forcibly removed her crown. De Silva needed hospital treatment after the incident, seen by stunned spectators in a packed venue as well as a live social media audience. To qualify for the title, contestants must be married. De Silva is estranged from her husband, but they are still legally married. I have chosen mango flavor, pistachio flavor and strawberry flavor for the ice creams for this recipe but you can use other flavors as well. I have used some crushed mango, strawberry and pistachio to add extra flavor and texture to the recipe. Because of the variety of flavors in this ice cream this is a perfect recipe for parties and celebrations.#CassataIceCream #CassataRecipe #CassataCakeFriends, please do try this cassata ice cream at home and share it with your friends and family.
